WEBVTT

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.000
HAS BROUGHT WITH IT
 THE LARGEST MOVEMENT OF PEOPLE

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.000
IN THE HISTORY OF MODERN TIMES.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.000
EVERYWHERE MILLIONS OF PEOPLE

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:29.000
ARE ON THEIR WAY
 TO SOMEWHERE NEW.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
NO WALL OR BARRIER IS
 STRONG ENOUGH TO STOP MIGRANTS

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.000
AS THEY CROSS
 INTERNATIONAL BORDERS

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.000
ON A JOURNEY
 TO WHERE THE ACTION IS:

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.000
THE GLOBAL CITIES.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.000
LOCATED AT THE CENTER OF EUROPE

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.000
AND THE HEART OF GERMANY,

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.000
FRANKFURT IS THE GERMAN CITY

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:52.000
WITH THE LARGEST
 FOREIGN POPULATION.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:55.000
HERE ONE OUT OF THREE
 INHABITANTS IS A FOREIGNER.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.000
IMMIGRATION IS SURGING
 IN FRANKFURT

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.000
AND THE REST OF THE COUNTRY.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.000
ALREADY ALMOST
 10 MILLION PEOPLE IN GERMANY

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:02.000
ARE IMMIGRANTS.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:04.000
THIS IS INSPIRING
 RIGHT-WING POLITICIANS

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:07.000
TO PANDER TO XENOPHOBIC
 ATTITUDES TO WIN VOTERS.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:09.000
RECENTLY, IN A FRANKFURT SUBURB

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:11.000
A FAR RIGHT PARTY
 CALLED THE REPUBLICANS

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:13.000
HELD A CONVENTION TO OUTLINE

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:16.000
TO WHAT IN ESSENCE IS
 AN ANTI-IMMIGRATION PLATFORM.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.000
[MAN TRANSLATING SCHLIERER]

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.000
WE CANNOT ACCEPT

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.000
ANY MORE IMMIGRANTS.

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:21.000
GERMANY SHOULD INSTEAD

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.000
SHIP BACK
 TO THEIR OWN COUNTRIES

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:25.000
THE FOREIGNERS
 THAT HAVE PROVEN

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.000
UNWILLING TO INTEGRATE
 INTO THIS COUNTRY.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:32.000
[CROWD CHANTING IN GERMAN]

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:34.000
NARRATOR: BUT THE
 ALARMISTRHETORIC ON THE RIGHT

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:35.000
IS ALSO BEING COUNTERED

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.000
BY ANOTHER STRONGLY HELD VIEW

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.000
THAT GERMANY NEEDS IMMIGRANTS

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.000
TO ENSURE
 ITS FUTURE ECONOMIC GROWTH.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:43.000
WE DO NOT HAVE ENOUGH
EDUCATED PEOPLE

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:47.000
IN ORDER TO CULTIVATE AND FOSTER

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:49.000
THE NEW ECONOMY IN THIS COUNTRY.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:52.000
SO, WE NEED FOREIGN,

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.000
EDUCATED, WELL-INFORMED PEOPLE

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:57.000
IN ORDER TO HELP US
 TO ESTABLISH AND CREATE

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:59.000
THE ENVIRONMENT
 FOR A GERMAN NEW ECONOMY.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.000
NARRATOR: FRANKFURT IS THE
 HUB OF THE GERMAN NEW ECONOMY

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:05.000
AND A GLOBAL FINANCIAL CENTER.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:08.000
ALMOST 400 INTERNATIONAL BANKS
 HAVE OFFICES HERE.

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.000
FRANKFURT IS ALSO HEADQUARTERS

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.000
OF THE EUROPEAN CENTRAL BANK

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:14.000
WHERE PEOPLE FROM 15 COUNTRIES

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:16.000
ARE ATTEMPTING TO FORGE
 A COMMON IDENTITY.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.000
ACTUALLY IT'S A GREAT THING

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:22.000
TO HAVE A GROUP OF PEOPLE HERE,

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:24.000
WHICH IS STILL
VERY MUCH EXPANDING,

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:27.000
COMING FROM
 THE 15 MEMBER STATES

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:28.000
OF THE EUROPEAN UNION.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.000
[MAN TRANSLATING HOPPENSTEDT]

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.000
IN OUR WORK CONTRACT

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:33.000
THERE IS A CLAUSE
 WHICH RECOGNIZES

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:35.000
OUR INDIVIDUAL
 NATIONAL IDENTITY,

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:37.000
BUT IN ADDITION,
 IT ALSO ESTABLISHES

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:39.000
OUR LINKS
 WITH THE EUROPEAN UNION,

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:42.000
OUR CITIZENSHIP
 OF THE EUROPEAN UNION.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:44.000
[MAN TRANSLATING CHAILLOUX]

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:46.000
MAYBE IN 10 OR 15 YEARS

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:48.000
GERMANS, ITALIANS, FRENCH,

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:50.000
WILL SLOWLY BEGIN TO LOSE

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.000
THEIR INDIVIDUAL
 NATIONAL IDENTITY.

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:54.000
THAT'S TRUE.
 BUT FOR THE MOMENT

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.000
THE REALITY IS
 THAT WE ARE WHO WE ARE.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:58.000
AND WE'RE NOT YET
 BLENDING TOGETHER

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:01.000
OUR NATIONAL DIFFERENCES.

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:05.000
NARRATOR: JUST LIKE AT
 THE EUROPEAN CENTRAL BANK

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:07.000
IN FRANKFURT
 GERMANS AND NON-GERMANS

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:10.000
ARE ALSO TRYING
 TO FIND A COMMON IDENTITY.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.000
BUT IT OFTEN SEEMS THAT
 NOT EVEN PEACEFUL CO-EXISTENCE

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:14.000
IS YET POSSIBLE.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:17.000
[WOMAN TRANSLATING]

