BECAUSE THEY MAKE
 TOO MANY KIDS

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.000
AND THEY TAKE MANY THINGS AWAY
 FROM THE GERMAN PEOPLE,

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:25.000
LIKE JOBS AND APARTMENTS.

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:27.000
[WOMAN TRANSLATING
 WOLF-ALMANASREH]

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:30.000
FOR US, AN ANTI-DISCRIMINATION
 STRATEGY IN FRANKFURT

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:32.000
IS EXTREMELY IMPORTANT,

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:34.000
BECAUSE THERE IS LOTS OF IT

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:37.000
AND OFTEN PEOPLE DON'T EVEN
 REALIZE THEY'RE DISCRIMINATING.

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:40.000
NARRATOR:
 THE FRANKFURT DEPARTMENT

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:41.000
FOR MULTICULTURAL AFFAIRS,

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:43.000
A UNIQUE EXPERIMENT IN GERMANY,

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:46.000
IS IMPLEMENTING ITS
 ANTI-DISCRIMINATION STRATEGY

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.000
THROUGH TRAINING WORKSHOPS

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:49.000
WITH THE FRANKFURT
 POLICE DEPARTMENT.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:53.000
[WOMAN TRANSLATING
 WOLF-ALMANASREH]

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:55.000
IN THE FIRST PLACE,
 THE WORKSHOPS

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.000
WITH THE FRANKFURT POLICE

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:58.000
ARE MEANT TO SENSITIZE
 OUR POLICE FORCE

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:01.000
IN ITS DEALINGS
 WITH FOREIGNERS AND IMMIGRANTS.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:03.000
AND MORE IMPORTANTLY,

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:05.000
TO PREVENT
 ANY KIND OF POLICE ABUSES

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.000
AGAINST FOREIGNERS.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:11.000
[MAN TRANSLATING BERNHARDT]

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:13.000
IN THESE WORKSHOPS
 BOTH FOREIGNERS AND GERMANS

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:17.000
ARE LEARNING MUTUAL
 UNDERSTANDING BETWEEN CULTURES

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:20.000
AND THIS HOPEFULLY WILL LEAD
 TO A MORE TOLERANT BEHAVIOR

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:22.000
ON BOTH SIDES.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.000
NARRATOR: THE ANTI-
 DISCRIMINATION STRATEGY

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:30.000
OF THE FRANKFURT DEPARTMENT
 FOR MULTI-CULTURAL AFFAIRS

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:32.000
IS ALREADY VISIBLE
 ON THE STREETS.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.000
IN FRANKFURT,
 UNLIKE OTHER GERMAN CITIES,

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:38.000
NON-GERMANS ARE PERMITTED
 TO JOIN THE POLICE FORCE.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:39.000
[MAN TRANSLATING BENZ]

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:41.000
I DON'T MAKE DISTINCTIONS

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.000
BETWEEN MY GERMAN
 AND FOREIGN COLLEAGUES.

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:44.000
MY PARTNER'S PARENTS
 ARE TURKISH,

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:46.000
BUT FOR ME
 HE'S NOT A FOREIGNER,

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:49.000
HE'S MY PARTNER, MY FRIEND.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:52.000
[CROWD CHANTING]

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:54.000
[MAN TRANSLATING BRANCO]

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:56.000
IT SHOULDN'T MATTER

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:58.000
IF A PLAYER'S
 BLACK, WHITE OR RED.

00:04:58.000 --> 00:05:01.000
I WANT TO ASK FANS EVERYWHERE

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:04.000
TO HAVE THE COURAGE
 TO SUPPORT PLAYERS

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.000
WITHOUT LOOKING AT THEIR COLOR.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.000
[MAN TRANSLATING]
 I THINK 40 PERCENT

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:13.000
OF THE PLAYERS IN THE GERMAN
 FIRST DIVISION ARE FOREIGNERS.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:17.000
I CAN'T IMAGINE GERMAN FOOTBALL
 WITHOUT FOREIGN PLAYERS.

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:19.000
NARRATOR: INDEED GERMANY
 IS EMBARKING ON A TURNAROUND

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:21.000
IN ITS 25-YEAR-OLD POLICY

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:23.000
OF STRICTLY
 LIMITING IMMIGRATION.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:27.000
GERMANY IS A COUNTRY THAT
CHANGES AND EVOLVES SLOWLY

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:30.000
AND AT CERTAIN POINTS

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:34.000
IT REACHES A LEVEL WHERE
A BIG CHANGE HAPPENS QUICKLY.

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:36.000
AND I THINK THAT'S
 WHAT WE'RE NEARING

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:39.000
IN THE IMMIGRATION THING.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.000
NARRATOR: IN FRANKFURT
 ATTITUDES TO IMMIGRATION

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:42.000
ARE INDEED CHANGING,

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:44.000
BECAUSE LIKE
 OTHER GLOBAL CITIES,

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.000
FRANKFURT IS SWITCHING
 FROM AN OLD INDUSTRIAL ECONOMY

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:48.000
TO A NEW
 TECHNOLOGY-DRIVEN ECONOMY

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:50.000
AND THERE IS A LABOR SHORTAGE,

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:52.000
ESPECIALLY
 IN THE CONSTRUCTION INDUSTRY.

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:55.000
NEW, INTERNATIONAL COMPANIES
 ARE MOVING INTO THE CITY,

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:57.000
CREATING A HIGH DEMAND
 FOR OFFICE SPACE.

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:59.000
TO COPE WITH THIS DEMAND,

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:01.000
THE CITY OF FRANKFURT
 HAS PREPARED A PLAN.

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:03.000
THIS IS A MASTER PLAN

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:06.000
AND IT'S CALLED
"FRANKFURT 2000."

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:09.000
THE CONTENT IS 50 NEW PLACES

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:11.000
FOR HIGH-RISINGS.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:15.000
AND IN THIS "FRANKFURT 2000"

00:06:15.000 --> 00:06:18.000
ONE OF THE FIRST
 HIGH-RISINGS WE BUILT

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:21.000
IS THE URBAN
 ENTERTAINMENT CENTER.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.000
[WOMAN TRANSLATING
 WOLF-ALMANASREH]

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:26.000
I THINK THE NEW ECONOMY
 IN FRANKFURT

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:30.000
IS BEING BUILT ON THE SHOULDERS
 OF IMMIGRANTS AND FOREIGNERS.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:34.000
NARRATOR: THE PROBLEM
 IN THE CONSTRUCTION INDUSTRY

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.000
IS THAT MANY
 OF THE IMMIGRANTS' SHOULDERS

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:38.000
ARE IN FRANKFURT ILLEGALLY.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.000
IN THE FIRST
 NINE MONTHS OF 2000

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:43.000
INSPECTORS OF THE GERMAN
 MINISTRY OF LABOR

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:47.000
HAVE RAIDED 2300 CONSTRUCTION
 SITES IN THE FRANKFURT AREA.

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:53.000
[MAN TRANSLATING SKOPPKE]

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:55.000
THESE FOREIGN WORKERS
 HAVE NOTHING TO FEAR

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:57.000
IF THEY HAVE
 A VALID WORK PERMIT.

00:06:57.000 --> 00:07:00.000
WHAT WE WANT TO KNOW
 ARE THEIR WORKING CONDITIONS.

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:02.000
WHO PAYS THEM, WHO HIRES THEM,

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:04.000
AND WHERE
 THESE WORKERS COME FROM.

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:09.000
[MAN TRANSLATING GRIESHEIMER]

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:11.000
WITH A CHANGE IN THE LAW
 WE NOW HAVE THE AUTHORITY

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:14.000
TO HOLD THE CONSTRUCTION
 COMPANY RESPONSIBLE

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:17.000
IF ITS SUBCONTRACTORS
 EMPLOY ILLEGAL FOREIGN WORKERS.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:20.000
COMPANIES CAN NO LONGER
 HIDE BEHIND SUBCONTRACTORS

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.000
AND PRETEND
 THEY HAVE NOTHING TO DO

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:26.000
WITH THE ILLEGAL
 FOREIGN WORKERS PROBLEM.

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.000
NARRATOR: CONSTRUCTION WORKERS
 ARE NOT THE ONLY FOREIGNERS

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:30.000
COMING TO FRANKFURT
 TO WORK ILLEGALLY.

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:32.000
AN ESTIMATED
 5,000 FOREIGN WOMEN

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.000
ARRIVE IN FRANKFURT EVERY YEAR

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:35.000
TO WORK IN THE SEX INDUSTRY.

