THERE'S A REAL NEED
 FOR FOREIGN WOMEN

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.000
TO WORK AS PROSTITUTES,

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:43.000
BECAUSE THEY'RE
 THE ONES PROVIDING

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:46.000
MOST OF THE 12,600
 SEXUAL SERVICES

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:48.000
SOUGHT AFTER
 IN THIS CITY EVERY DAY.

