I ENTERED GERMANY
 THROUGH THE FRANKFURT AIRPORT.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:17.000
WITH 2,500 DOLLARS IN MY PURSE

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:20.000
AND HOPEFULLY LOTS OF LUCK.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:25.000
NARRATOR:
 THE FRANKFURT AIRPORT

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:26.000
IS ONE OF THE BUSIEST
 IN THE WORLD.

