50 MILLION PASSENGERS COME
 THROUGH THIS AIRPORT EVERY YEAR

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:33.000
AND NO ONE KNOWS HOW MANY
 OF THEM ARE ILLEGAL IMMIGRANTS.

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:35.000
[MAN TRANSLATING KR GER]

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:37.000
WE'RE IMPLEMENTING
 MANY CONTROL MEASURES

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:41.000
TO HELP US IN OUR FIGHT
 AGAINST ILLEGAL IMMIGRANTS.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.000
TO BE SUCCESSFUL

00:08:42.000 --> 00:08:45.000
ANY COUNTRY NEEDS A HIGHLY
 TRAINED BORDER POLICE,

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:48.000
AS WELL AS
 A SOPHISTICATED INFRASTRUCTURE

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.000
AND TECHNOLOGY TO BACK YOU UP.

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:55.000
IN FRANKFURT AIRPORT
 WE HAVE ALL OF IT.

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:57.000
[WOMAN TRANSLATING PROSTITUTE]

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:59.000
AT THE AIRPORT
 I ALWAYS GET NERVOUS,

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:01.000
'CAUSE I'M COLOMBIAN.

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:05.000
AND COLOMBIANS
 ARE HASSLED EVERYWHERE.

