SO THERE'S AN X-RAY
 AND CHECKING THE BAGS

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:09.000
AND QUESTIONS ABOUT DRUGS

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:12.000
AND WHY YOU'RE COMING
 TO FRANKFURT.

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:14.000
SO I THINK IT'S NATURAL
 TO GET NERVOUS.

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.000
[MAN TRANSLATING KR GER]

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:19.000
WE USE INTERVIEWING TECHNIQUES

00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:21.000
DEVELOPED IN
 OUR TRAINING PROGRAMS

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:22.000
OVER MANY YEARS.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:24.000
BUT WE MOSTLY RELY
 ON THE HIGH EXPERTISE

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:26.000
OF OUR FRONTLINE INSPECTORS.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:30.000
THEY NEVER MAKE A DECISION
 BASED ONLY ON AN INTERVIEW,

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:32.000
THEY ALSO TAKE INTO ACCOUNT
 THE PERSONALITY

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:35.000
AND BEHAVIOR OF THE PASSENGER.

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:37.000
AND OF COURSE,
 THEY LOOK VERY CLOSELY

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:40.000
AT PASSPORTS
 AND OTHER DOCUMENTS.

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:42.000
[WOMAN TRANSLATING PROSTITUTE]

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:44.000
I TELL IMMIGRATION
 I'M A TOURIST.

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:47.000
ALL THE GIRLS I WORK WITH
 SAY THEY'RE TOURISTS

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:49.000
AND I ONLY STAY THREE MONTHS
 IN FRANKFURT,

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:51.000
LIKE ANY OTHER TOURIST.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:54.000
AT THE AIRPORT THERE'S
 NO SPANISH TRANSLATOR.

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:56.000
THEY SPEAK GERMAN
 AND I DON'T UNDERSTAND,

00:09:56.000 --> 00:09:59.000
SO I JUST SHOW THEM
 THE $2,500 THEY REQUIRE

00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:02.000
AND SAY "NO COKE"
 AND I'M IN.

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:07.000
NARRATOR: AS LONG
 AS THERE IS A DEMAND,

00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:09.000
FOREIGN WOMEN WILL CONTINUE
 TO COME TO FRANKFURT

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.000
AS PROSTITUTES.

00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:11.000
AND ON THE STREETS

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:13.000
THEY WILL MIX WITH THOUSANDS
 OF OTHER FOREIGN WOMEN

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:14.000
WHO'VE COME TO FRANKFURT

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:17.000
TO WORK AS HIGHLY-TRAINED
 PROFESSIONALS.

